Project Introduction
--------------------------------------------------------------------

The webqureypy is a web qurey tool written in Python, it can query 
the useful information from the web and show it or send it to sms

Author: Wisilence Seol ( wisicn AT gmail Dot com )

Project Home Page: http://code.google.com/p/webquerypy/

development mailing list: webquerypy-project-development@googlegroups.com

Discuss group:
https://groups.google.com/group/webquerypy-project-development/

Questions, comments, feature requests ,bug report and patches are most welcome.



Files/Modules Introduction
--------------------------------------------------------------------
This package contain the following files:

handleHTTP.py: 
	a module to fetch the raw html page from the web and use regexp 
	to find the match lines

LICENSE:
	This project's License File.
	
PyFetion.py:
	a 3rd part module ,it can use the China Mobile Fetion to send out the sms, 
        from http://code.google.com/p/pytool/, thanks the author cocobear.cn.
pySMS.py: 
	a module to easily invoke  PyFetion and send out the sms
README: 
	this file
sendSMS-sample.sh: 
	a Bash shell script to invoke the smsWeathe.py to sendout the weather SMS,
	just a sample
smsWeather.py:
	a module invoke the weatherQuery.py to get the weahter for a city,and sent it via PyFetion
stockQuery.py:
	a module to get a city's (cities') weather from http://www.weather.com.cn/ 
weatherQuery.py
        a module to get a stock's 'real time' price from http://www.google.com/finance




